                   </p>
                   <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3">
                       <a href="/orders" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg mt-3 mx-2">Go to My Orders</a>
                       <a href="/shop" class="btn btn-outline-danger btn-lg mt-3 mx-2">Back to Shop</a>
                   </div>
               </div>
           </div>
       </div>
   </div>
</div>

